This paper deals with the problem of vision-and-language navigation, which involves natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes methods that involve machine learning and optimization, which are relevant to categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with computer vision, which is relevant to categories such as cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.RO (Robotics).
